{"type":null,"faqId":18722,"title":"如何成为银卡会员用户，如何注册？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.19444445in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.0006944in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">  </span><span>首次开机导航界面有会员注册页面自动提醒</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">  </span><span>进入华为手机会员激活页面，点击立即激活</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=62993\" style=\"width:1.8798611in;height:3.3409722in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">  </span><span>点击注册，使用当前手机号注册，能够自动读取验证码，点击一下步</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=62994\" style=\"width:1.3180555in;height:2.3423612in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=62995\" style=\"width:1.3201389in;height:2.3430555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">  </span><span>注册成功，完成开机向导，进入手机-&gt;设置-&gt;华为云服务-&gt;点击华为账号，在帐号详情</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=62996\" style=\"width:1.3222222in;height:2.351389in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=62997\" style=\"width:1.2923611in;height:2.2979167in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=62998\" style=\"width:1.2881944in;height:2.2951388in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">  </span><span>当前帐号为银卡会员信息及银卡会员特权【预约服务、快修服务、应用市场开机礼包银卡版、游戏中心开机礼包银卡版、免费赠送160G网盘1年使用权】</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1786","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422260333000,"seriesProductName":"Cherry-CL10,CherryPlus-TL00,CherryPlus-TL00H,CherryPlus-TL00M,CherryPlus-TL10,CherryPlus-UL00,CherryPlus-UL10","visitedTimes":253,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}